message.content: ∀ {α : Type u_1} [inst : AddMonoid α] [inst_1 : HasEven α] [inst_2 : HasOdd α] {a b : α}, Odd a → Odd b → Even (a + b)

∀ {α : Type u_1} [inst : AddCommMonoid α] [inst_1 : HasOne α] [inst_2 : HasZero α],
  ∀ {l : List α}, (∀ x ∈ l, Odd x) → Even (l.sum)
∀ {α : Type u_2} [inst : Semiring α] {a b : α}, Odd a → Odd b → Even (a + b)

∀ {α : Type u_1} [inst : AddCommMonoid α] [inst_1 : HasOne α] [inst_2 : HasMul α] {s : Finset α}, 
  (∀ x ∈ s, Odd x) → Even (∑ x in s, x)
∀ {α : Type u_1} [inst : AddCommMonoid α] [inst_1 : HasOdd α] {s : Finset α}, (∀ x ∈ s, Odd x) → Even (s.sum id)

∀ {α : Type u_1} [inst : AddCommMonoid α] [inst_1 : HasOne α] [inst_2 : HasSmul ℕ α] {m : ℕ} {f : Fin m → α},
  (∀ i, Odd (f i)) → Even (∑ i, f i)
∀ {α : Type u_1} [inst : Semiring α] {a b : α}, Odd a → Odd b → Even (a + b)
